## 13. Hero-Flow for Media Capture

1. Load `/demos/art-print-storefront/` -- gallery renders with 12 print cards
2. Arrow-click scrolls gallery right (shows scroll is wired)
3. Click first print card -- product page loads
4. Select a size (e.g., 16x20) -- price updates
5. Click "Add to Cart" -- toast appears, nav badge shows 1
6. Click cart icon -- cart modal opens showing the item
7. Click "Proceed to Checkout" -- login modal appears
8. Enter email + password -- login succeeds, checkout POST fires
9. Order confirmation screen: order ID, email, shipping estimate
10. Open coaching panel on gallery page -- tab 1 shows Liquid prompt

